sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor A as Admin
    participant F as Frontend
    participant S as Auth Service
    participant M as MongoDB
    participant C as Redis

    Note over A,C: Audit Logs — GET /admin/audit-logs

    A->>F: Hap panelin e adminit
    F->>S: GET /admin/audit-logs (Bearer token)
    S->>S: Verifiko tokenin dhe rolin

    alt Jo i autentikuar
        S-->>F: 401 Pa leje
        F-->>A: Ridrejto te login
    else Nuk është admin
        S-->>F: 403 E ndaluar
        F-->>A: Trego gabimin
    else Admin i vlefshëm
        S->>M: Merr logs me filtra dhe paginim
        M-->>S: Lista e logs
        S-->>F: 200 {items, total, page, limit}
        F-->>A: Shfaq tabelën e logs
    end

    Note over A,C: Debug Redis — GET /admin/debug/redis/health

    A->>F: Kliko "Kontrollo Redis"
    F->>S: GET /admin/debug/redis/health (Bearer token)
    S->>C: Testo SET + GET + DELETE
    C-->>S: OK
    S-->>F: 200 {status: ok, connected: true}
    F-->>A: Redis funksionon

    Note over A,C: Debug Cache — Kontrollo Challenge dhe 2FA Setup

    A->>F: Kërko challenge ose 2FA setup
    F->>S: GET /admin/debug/login-challenge/{id}
    S->>C: Kontrollo nëse ekziston në Redis
    C-->>S: Vlera / null
    S-->>F: 200 {exists, ttlSeconds}
    F-->>A: Trego statusin e cache